, skeletal keel; 
tc
, trunck coelom; 
tlm
, trunk longitudinal muscles; 
vs
, ventral septum. Scale bars: A, E, F = 500 μm; B, C = 100 μm; D, G, H = 250 μm.

FIGURE 3.
